00:34:45.350 --> 00:34:48.880 align:middle line:90%
Now, let's look at waves.

00:34:48.880 --> 00:34:52.630 align:middle line:84%
The wave hit the
slit and radiate out,

00:34:52.630 --> 00:34:56.440 align:middle line:84%
striking the back wall
with the most intensity

00:34:56.440 --> 00:34:59.860 align:middle line:90%
directly in line with the slit.

00:34:59.860 --> 00:35:02.680 align:middle line:84%
The line of brightness
