00:35:32.890 --> 00:35:34.300 align:middle line:90%
the bright lines.

00:35:34.300 --> 00:35:37.090 align:middle line:84%
And where they cancel,
there is nothing.

00:35:37.090 --> 00:35:43.520 align:middle line:84%
So when we throw things, that
