00:35:53.500 --> 00:35:55.250 align:middle line:90%
Good so far.

00:35:55.250 --> 00:35:57.640 align:middle line:90%
Now, let's go quantum.

00:35:57.640 --> 00:36:03.180 align:middle line:90%


00:36:03.180 --> 00:36:10.680 align:middle line:84%
