00:36:30.190 --> 00:36:32.410 align:middle line:90%
An interference pattern.

00:36:32.410 --> 00:36:37.080 align:middle line:84%
We fired electrons, tiny
bits of matter through,

00:36:37.080 --> 00:36:41.740 align:middle line:84%
