00:36:48.910 --> 00:36:51.230 align:middle line:90%
It doesn't make sense.

00:36:51.230 --> 00:36:53.890 align:middle line:90%
But physicists are clever.

00:36:53.890 --> 00:36:56.650 align:middle line:84%
They thought, maybe
those little balls

00:36:56.650 --> 00:37:00.430 align:middle line:84%
are bouncing off each other
