00:37:04.420 --> 00:37:05.830 align:middle line:90%
at a time.

00:37:05.830 --> 00:37:10.140 align:middle line:84%
There is no way they could
interfere with each other.

00:37:10.140 --> 00:37:13.650 align:middle line:84%
But after an hour of this,
the same interference pattern

00:37:13.650 --> 00:37:15.140 align:middle line:90%
is seen to emerge.

00:37:15.140 --> 00:37:17.890 align:middle line:90%
The conclusion is inescapable.

00:37:17.890 --> 00:37:21.070 align:middle line:84%
The single electron
leaves as a particle,

00:37:21.070 --> 00:37:25.130 align:middle line:84%
becomes a wave of potentials,
goes through both slits,

00:37:25.130 --> 00:37:29.980 align:middle line:84%
and interferes with itself to
hit the wall like a particle.

00:37:29.980 --> 00:37:32.440 align:middle line:84%
But mathematically,
it's even stranger.

00:37:32.440 --> 00:37:36.430 align:middle line:84%
It goes through both slits
and it goes through neither.

00:37:36.430 --> 00:37:40.390 align:middle line:84%
And it goes through just one and
it goes through just the other.

00:37:40.390 --> 00:37:43.420 align:middle line:84%
All of these possibilities
are in superposition

00:37:43.420 --> 00:37:44.440 align:middle line:90%
with each other.

00:37:44.440 --> 00:37:47.290 align:middle line:84%
But physicists were
completely baffled by this,

00:37:47.290 --> 00:37:50.350 align:middle line:84%
so they decided to
peek and see which

00:37:50.350 --> 00:37:54.160 align:middle line:90%
slit it actually goes through.

00:37:54.160 --> 00:37:57.000 align:middle line:84%
They put a measuring
device by one slit

00:37:57.000 --> 00:38:02.290 align:middle line:84%
to see which one it went
through and let it fly.

00:38:02.290 --> 00:38:05.590 align:middle line:84%
But the quantum world
is far more mysterious

00:38:05.590 --> 00:38:07.660 align:middle line:90%
than they could have imagined.

00:38:07.660 --> 00:38:11.350 align:middle line:84%
When they observed,
the electron went back

00:38:11.350 --> 00:38:13.390 align:middle line:84%
to behaving like
a little marble.

00:38:13.390 --> 00:38:17.770 align:middle line:84%
It produced a pattern of two
bands, not an interference

00:38:17.770 --> 00:38:19.880 align:middle line:90%
pattern of many.

00:38:19.880 --> 00:38:25.010 align:middle line:84%
The very act of
measuring or observing

00:38:25.010 --> 00:38:27.950 align:middle line:84%
which split it went
through meant it only

00:38:27.950 --> 00:38:31.490 align:middle line:90%
went through one, not both.

00:38:31.490 --> 00:38:37.360 align:middle line:84%
The electron decided to act
differently as though it

00:38:37.360 --> 00:38:41.540 align:middle line:90%
was aware it was being watched.

00:38:41.540 --> 00:38:45.380 align:middle line:84%
And it was here that
physicists stepped forever

00:38:45.380 --> 00:38:49.601 align:middle line:84%
into the strange neverworld
