00:57:58.448 --> 00:58:02.939 align:middle line:84%
>> Our snowflake exhibit
comes to us from Japan and Mr.

00:58:02.939 --> 00:58:04.436 align:middle line:90%
Masaru Emoto.

00:58:04.436 --> 00:58:07.820 align:middle line:84%
Mr. Emoto became
terribly interested

00:58:07.820 --> 00:58:12.410 align:middle line:84%
